<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Pathien, Nang zainem pen,
 Hehpih a dim na hi;
 Na vangsakna lopi pen,
 A chungu ah vukin;
 Na lopina en kawmin,
 Na vangsakna chang leu;
 Thih chana umkhawm dingin,
 A thutiem uh det hen.

[V2]
 2. Khawvel a Na lenlai khan,
 Kana khuo Na hung tung;
 Kichenna kipahpih in,
 Uain Na supung tai;
 Tu-a a kichennau hi,
 Kipahpih in vang pie'n;
 A kideihnau hung pung hen,
 Na min le zah u hen.

[V3]
 3. Nicheng a Nang hun ging di'n,
 Aw Lalpa, panpih in;
 Lungkham, buoina a thuok un,
 Nangin thuokpih zelin
 A damlai niu hung tumin,
 Khawvel taihsan mahleu;
 Kumsawt a um khawm dingin,
 Na In ah pui inla.</lyrics>
<title>BLESS THEM O LORD</title>
</song>